          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Optimizing Performance with Chatterbox API A"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Monitor latency and throughput using Chatterbox's built-in metrics or integrate with tools like Prometheus. Cache frequent responses where appropriate, but invalidate cache on model updates. Use connection pooling to reduce overhead, and set timeouts (e.g., 30 seconds) to prevent hanging requests. For high-traffic scenarios, deploy multiple API keys across regions to balance load and ensure low latency."
